de.hsbremen.tc.tnc.message

Interface Combined<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the object type, that will be stacked
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PaReader, PaWriter, PbReader, PbWriter, PtTlsReader, PtTlsWriter

    public interface Combined<T>
    Generic helper to enable arbitrary message related objects to be stacked together via add and remove operations.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void add(Long vendorId, Long messageType, T component)
      Adds an object to the combined type for the related message type with the given vendor ID and and type ID.
      void remove(Long vendorId, Long messageType)
      Removes the object from the combined type for the related message type with the given vendor ID and and type ID.
